summaries.short: Alex and Tina invite themselves to Brett's movie premiere and meet a producer; Michelle has a night to herself.
summaries.full: Brett's invite to a movie premiere leads to an impromptu night on the town for everyone. Tina and Alex engage in a personal 'mission,' Brett looks to mend a work relationship and Michelle meets David, a divorced dad who wants to start a new charter school. Brett finds a way to cheer up Alex.

summaries.short: Tina returns to Houston with Alex and finds herself jealous; Brett and Michelle struggle through an intimate night.
summaries.full: Alex and Tina fly back to Houston to pack up her things. During a night of drinks and dancing, Tina finds herself unexpectedly jealous of Alex. Back in LA, Brett whisks Michelle away for some much-needed intimacy.

summaries.short: Michelle tries to spice things up with Brett; Alex helps Tina with her business and in exchange she vows to get him in shape.
summaries.full: Tina tries to shake Alex out of his funk by enlisting him to help her with her business and vowing to help him get the career of his dreams. Brett gets in trouble at work when his creative instincts rub co-workers the wrong way. Tina convinces Michelle to spice things up in the bedroom.

summaries.short: Series Premiere. Struggling actor Alex moves in with couple Brett and Michelle, while Michelle's sister Tina faces her own crossroads.
summaries.full: Series Premiere. After a struggling actor named Alex is evicted, his best friend Brett, a sound designer who's married with a wife and two kids, tries to convince Alex to stay in LA. Brett's wife Michelle deals with her directionless sister Tina. Following a group outing at the beach, Michelle and Brett clash while Tina confronts an ex, with the aid of Alex.
